    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ストーリー完結！プレイ時間は50時間以上！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ケモノがムチムチする系コマンドRPG、「WhiteClothes」がついに完結！！女神と呼ばれる謎の生命体が世界を浄化する。ミルネよ、姉妹を、そして世界を救え！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >笑いあり、涙あり、お腹いっぱい、胸いっぱいの冒険を続けよう！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/05c3bd8dcd0379cb2bcfcea68a0ac800.avif?t=1769347805\" width=1280 height=480 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新しい能力！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >強力なスキル、パッシブ、装備を多数実装ッ！バトルをさらに派手に、奥深く！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >もっとも...。強力になっているのは敵も同じだがね...。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/3d2ed68fd1d250af92caa96f68e63309.poster.avif?t=1769347805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/3d2ed68fd1d250af92caa96f68e63309.webm?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/3d2ed68fd1d250af92caa96f68e63309.mp4?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>新しいキャラクター！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >シラタマをはじめとした新しいキャラクターたちが参戦！既存のキャラクターにはないユニークな特性を持っている！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >どんなキャラかは使ってみてのお楽しみ！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/b8bb122dca8788cd370ed6c6735d8160.poster.avif?t=1769347805\" width=162 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/b8bb122dca8788cd370ed6c6735d8160.webm?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/b8bb122dca8788cd370ed6c6735d8160.mp4?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/2951cd7e4c27032360874e045eb574de.poster.avif?t=1769347805\" width=262 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/2951cd7e4c27032360874e045eb574de.webm?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>世界観を盛り上げる会話劇！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >キャラそれぞれの個性が立った会話もたっぷり楽しめる！中には倫理観の終わっている奴もいるので注意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/aa260bb3519be8e51ee06523a9e6725a.poster.avif?t=1769347805\" width=1170 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/aa260bb3519be8e51ee06523a9e6725a.webm?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/aa260bb3519be8e51ee06523a9e6725a.mp4?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NPCを支配せよ！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >フィールド上のNPCの大半を洗脳してシモベとして従えることが可能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本当は悪いことだけど、皆にはナイショだよ♪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/6436c49c1c0935870bb958d457fa7460.poster.avif?t=1769347805\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/6436c49c1c0935870bb958d457fa7460.webm?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/6436c49c1c0935870bb958d457fa7460.mp4?t=1769347805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>シモベを知れ！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >洗脳したシモベは呼び出して様々なスキルで援護してくれる！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >収集要素として図鑑も実装！気になるあの子の意外な一面がわかるかも！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398510/extras/f32a24b8603df8d7ed4f73678845a593.avif?t=1769347805\" width=1280 height=720 /></span></p>",
